                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      When asked how many chickens and cows he had on his farm Mr Brown refused to answer directly, but he did say that the total number of heads was 30 and the total number of legs was 100 . How many of each was there?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Let the number of chickens $=x$ and number of cows $=y$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      A farmer has some chickens and some cows .He counted $30$ heads

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $ \begin{aligned} x + y = 30 \\ x = 30 - y \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Each chicken has 2 legs and cow has 4 legs

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $ \begin{aligned} 2x + 4y = 100 \\ x + 2y = 50 \\ 30 - y + 2y = 50 \\ y = 20 \text {cows} \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $ \begin{aligned} x = 30 - y \\ x = 30 - 20 \\ x = 10 \text {chickens} \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $10 \text{chickens}, 20 \text{cows}$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • I think of a number, divide it by $7$ and subtract $3$. The result is $6$. What was the number I first thought of?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Let the number be $x$,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              $ \begin{aligned} \dfrac {x} {7} - 3 &= 6 \\ \dfrac {x} {7} &= 6 + 3 \\ \dfrac {x} {7} &= 9 \\ x &= 9 \times 7 \\ x &= 63 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              $63$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • There is a number, $x$. When I add $7$ to $x$ then multiply the answer by $8$, the overall result is the same as just multiplying $x$ by 22. What is $x$?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                $ \begin{aligned} ( x + 7 ) \times 8 = x \times 22 \\ 8x + 56 = 22x \\ 22x - 8x = 56 \\ 14x = 56 \\ x = 4 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                $4$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • I think of a number, multiply it by $9$ and subtract $7$. The result is $101$. What was the number I first thought of?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Let the number $=a$,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $ \begin{aligned} (a \times 9) - 7 &= 101 \\ a \times 9 &= 108 \\ a &= \dfrac {108} {9} \\ a &= 12 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $12$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • There is a number, $x$. When I add $8$ to $x$ then multiply the answer by $6$, the overall result is the same as just multiplying $x$ by 18. What is $x$?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    $ \begin{aligned} x + 8 \times 8 &= x \times 18 \\ 8x + 64 &= 18x \\ 8x &= 64 \\ x &= 8 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    $8$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • I think of a number, divide it by $7$ and add $9$. The result is $17$. What was the number I first thought of?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Let the number $=a$,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $ \begin{aligned} a \div 7 + 9 &= 17 \\ a \div 7 &= 17 - 9 \\ a \div 7 &= 8 \\ a &= 8 \times 7 \\ a &= 56 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $56$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • There is a number, n. When I add 3 to n then multiply the answer by 4, the overall result is the same as just multiplying n by 6. What is n?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $ \begin{aligned} (n + 3 \times) 4 &= 6n \\ 4n + 12 &= 6n \\ 6n - 4n &= 12 \\ 2n &= 12 \\ n &= \dfrac {12} {2} \\ n &= \dfrac {6 \times 2} {2} \\ n &= \dfrac {6 \times \times {2}} {\times {2}} \\ n &= 6 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $6$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      To cook a joint of beef, you leave it in the oven for $30 \ \text{minutes}$ for every kilogram it weighs plus $20 \ \text{minutes}$ extra. Find how long you should cook a joint weighing:

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      %empty%

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      %empty%

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • $2 \ \text{kg}$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Time for 1 kg of joint of beef = $30$ minutes

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Time for extra 1 kg of joint of beef = $20$ minutes

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          As per the question,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          $ \begin{aligned} \text{Time taken for 2kg}&= 60 + 20 \ &= 80 \text{minutes} \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          For $2$ kg it takes $80$ minutes

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          $80 \text{minutes}$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • $3.5 \ \text{kg}$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Let time be x for $\dfrac {1}{2} \text{kg}$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Time for 1 kg of joint of beef = $30$ minutes

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Time for extra 1 kg of joint of beef = $20$ minutes

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            As per the question,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            $ \begin{aligned} \text{Let time be x for 3.5 kg} \ \text{then}\ \ & x = \dfrac {3.5 \times 30}{1} \\ & x = 150 \text{min} \\ \text{time} = 105+20\ \\ &= 125 \text{minutes} \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          For a film, the seats cost $\pounds 3$ for each child and $\pounds 7$ for each adult. I was charged $\pounds 51$ for all the seats I bought.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          %empty%

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          %empty%

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            • Did I buy more than $7$ adult tickets?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Cost of each child seat = $\pounds 3$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Cost of each Adult seat = $\pounds 7$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              As per the question,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              $ \begin{aligned} \text{let number of child seats = x} \ \text{let number of Adult seats = y} \ \text{Total cost = \pounds 51} \ 3x+7y=51 \ \text{No, we can't buy more than 7 Adult tickets because it will cost more than \pounds 51} \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              No

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • If there were more adult tickets than child tickets, how many of each did I buy?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                $ \begin{aligned} \text {As per the equation 3x+7y=51} \ & 3x+7y=51 \ & 3\times(3)+7\times(6)=51 \ & \pounds 51=\pounds 51 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                6 adult tickets and 3 child tickets

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • If there were more child tickets than adult tickets, how many of each did I buy?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $ \begin{aligned} \text {As per the equation 3x+7y=51} \ & 3x+7y=51 \ & 3\times(10)+7\times(21)=51 \ & \pounds 51=\pounds 51 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  3 adult tickets and 10 child tickets

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Eggs are sold in boxes of $12$, costing $\pounds 1.68$. I wish to make $15$ cakes for a local fete and the recipe requires that I use $5$ eggs for each cake.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                %empty%

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                %empty%

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • How many eggs will I use altogether if I make $15$ cakes?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    As per the question,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    number of Eggs per box =$12$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Costof each box = $\pounds 1.68$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Number of eggs per cake = $5$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Total number of cake = $15$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    $ \begin{aligned} \text{Let the number of eggs be x for 15 cakes} \ \text{then}\ \ & x = 15 \times 5 \ & x = 75 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    $75$ eggs will I use altogether if I make $15$ cakes

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    $75$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • How many boxes must I buy to ensure I have enough eggs to make the $15$ cakes?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      As per the question,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $ \begin{aligned} \text{Let the number of box be x for 75 Eggs} \ \text{then}\ \ & 75 = 12 \times x \ & x = \dfrac{75}{12} \ & x = 6.25 \approxeq 7 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $7$ boxes must I buy to ensure I have enough eggs to make the $15$ cakes

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $6.25 \approxeq 7$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      A box of Kiddimix contains $20$ chocolates of which $8$ are plain chocolates. If $16$ of the $20$ have soft centres, what can you say about how many plain chocolates there are with soft centres?

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      A box of Kiddimix contains $20$ chocolates.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      which $8$ are plain chocolates.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      As per the question,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $ \begin{aligned} \text{If 16 of the 20 have soft centres} \ \text{then} \ \ 20 - 16 = 4 \\ \text{4 of the 8 have plain chocolates} \ \text{then} \ \ 8 - 4 = 4 \\ \text{At least 4 plane chocolates have soft centres} \\ \text{plain chocolates there are with soft centres} \geq 4 \therefore 4 \leq x > 8 \end{aligned} $

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $4 \leq x > 8$

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Three friends went to a burger restaurant.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Tom had a burger and chips and he paid $\pounds 8.00$.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Fred had two burgers and a drink. Fred paid $\pounds 15.00$.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Jo had a burger and a drink. Jo paid $\pounds 8.50$.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Work out the cost of the burger, the chips and the drink.
